<title type="html"><![CDATA[5/16(Sat.) Oil prices crashed/ How Covid-19 could change the world (Host: Morris?)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=391&amp;p=408#p408"><![CDATA[
Session I: Why US oil prices crashed and how it will affect you<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.aljazeera.com/ajimpact/oil-prices-crash-affect-200421134650761.html">https://www.aljazeera.com/ajimpact/oil- ... 50761.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1. How much do you know about the oil prices crashed? What might be the key reasons for it?<br />2.Has there been any impact on you/Taiwan because of the crashed oil prices? <br />3.What will oil prices go in the future? Why?<br />4.What can we do to gain benefits from the oil prices crashed?<br /><br /><br />Session II: How Covid-19 could change the world?<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://think.ing.com/reports/pandenomics-how-covid-19-could-change-the-world/">https://think.ing.com/reports/pandenomi ... the-world/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.According to your observation, when will Covid-19 go away?  What/how will it, such as economy, technology, industry, national power, be changed afterwards?<br />2.Will you travel abroad for fun after Covid-19 relief?  Which countries/areas will be safer/better to travel to? Why or why not?<br />3.What did you gain/lose the most during Covid-19 pandemic period?  <br />4.What lessons or experiences have you learned from Covid-19?<br /><br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk<br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion<br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences<br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br />a minimum charge of Dante coffee for Royal English club attendant NT$80 (丹提低消80元)<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500.請帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=13721">morris</a> — Mon May 11, 2020 10:52 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
